g.text: 0x10 | size_t | length | Total bytes stored (offset + pending)
0x18 | size_t | offset | Index of next byte to send

ol.li: data + offset is the starting address for write() / send().
length - offset is the byte count for the syscall.
If offset == length, buffer is exhausted; reset offset = length = 0.
If offset > capacity / 2, perform memmove() to compact.
